                                           :OWLRL2DLAxioms "disjointUnionOf: SIMetricPrefixedUnit, SINonCoherentDerivedUnit" ;
                                           :elucidation "An SI unit whos numerical factor in front of the product of base SI units is NOT equal to one."@en ;
